Package: locatr
Title: Audit-Ready Geocoding and Local Geography for Messy Location Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("George", "Arthur", , "prigasgenthian48@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-1975-1459"))
Description: Cleans, geocodes, validates, reviews, and exports messy location
    address data supplied by the user. The package sits on top of
    'tidygeocoder': it calls geocoding services, rejects implausible coordinates
    with configurable region guards, applies fallback name/address matching,
    joins points to optional local geography with 'sf', and records an audit
    trail showing how each coordinate was produced. Outputs are designed for
    manual review, dashboards, and reusable location crosswalks.
